### 8. CRIAR UM NOVO AGENDAMENTO (para ocupar um horário)
# Use um token válido (cliente ou barbeiro)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

# Certifique-se que os IDs (clientId=1, barbershopId=1, barberId=1, serviceId=1) existem!
{
  "clientId": 1,
  "barbershopId": 1,
  "barberId": 1,
  "serviceId": 1,
  "date": "2025-12-20",
  "time": "14:30"
}

### -------------------------------------------

### 9. LISTAR AGENDAMENTOS DO CLIENTE ID 1
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/client/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### -------------------------------------------

### 10. LISTAR AGENDAMENTOS DA BARBEARIA ID 1
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/barbershop/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### -------------------------------------------

### 11. BUSCAR AGENDAMENTO PELO ID 1
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### -------------------------------------------

### 12. REAGENDAR O AGENDAMENTO ID 1
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/1/reschedule
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2025-12-22",
  "time": "15:00"
}

### -------------------------------------------

### 13. CANCELAR O AGENDAMENTO ID 1
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/4/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### -------------------------------------------

### 14. CONFIRMAR O AGENDAMENTO ID 1 (Crie um novo agendamento #8 antes se cancelou o #13)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/3/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### -------------------------------------------

### 15. COMPLETAR O AGENDAMENTO ID 1 (Execute após confirmar #14)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/3/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### -------------------------------------------

### 16. BUSCAR HORÁRIOS DISPONÍVEIS
# Use um token válido. Ajuste a data e o barbershopId conforme necessário.
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/available-slots?barbershopId=1&date=2025-12-20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}